quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  4,87,"Alla, dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa KaŇčko, ma o Moo…ďi on √Īande Darngal, sikke alaa e mayre. Alaa …ďur…óo gooŇču…óude Alla yeewtere ?"
  4,88,"Ko wa…ói on e fii …ďee naafiqii…ďe pe…óle …ói…ói ?! Ko Alla woni Uggin…óo …ďe sabu ko …ďe faggitii. E on paala feewnude oon mbo Alla Majjini ? Kala on mo Alla majjini, a he…ďantaa mo laawol.peewal"
  4,89,"He…ďe ngoo…óe sinno on njedduno wano no…ďe njddiri nih, laato…óon fot…ďe.e ma…ď…ďe wota on njogito e ma…ď…ďe weldii…ďe haa …ďe pera e laawol Alla ngol. Si …ďe nduŇčitii, nanngee …ďe mbaron …ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe.Wata on njogito e ma…ď…ďe weldi…ó…óo wonaa balloowo"
  4,90,"Si wanaa …ďen …ďe hino njokkoo faade e yim…ďe …ďe ahadi woni hakkunde mon e ma…ď…ďe, maa…óuum …ďe ngarii emon …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen no …ďi…ótanii ka…ďagol on, maa …ďe ka…ďa e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe. Si Alla Haajuno, O Wurtayno …ďe e dow moo…óon, …ďe ka…ďo on. Si …ďe pottitike on, …ďe ka…ďaaki on, …ďe werlike kisal e mon, haray Alla Wa…óanaali on e dow ma…ď…ďe laawol."
  4,91,"Arma tawon wo…ó…ďe goo muuy…ďe nde …ďe koolnorata on koolnora yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen. Tuma kala nde …ďe nduttaa e geddi …óin,…ďe cu∆ī∆īitee e nder majji. Si …ďe ngaccani on, …ďe mberloo kisal e mon, …ďe curi juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, nanngee …ďe mbaron …ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe. Ko …ďen …óon moo…óon, [woni ke Min] mba…óani on e ma…ď…ďe hujja …ďanngu…óo."